data.description: $15,000. from seller to help with debt payoff, closing costs, upgrades to the home or rate buy down.  Best Value in Mountain Home, Idaho! This charming stick-built home on a spacious 1-acre lot, offers a perfect blend of tranquility & scenic beauty. Minutes to Mountain Home Air Force Base, this property provides easy access to local amenities, & outdoor recreational opportunities. The best of both worlds with a peaceful, rural setting while being close to town. The well-designed floor plan creates a warm inviting atmosphere, with plenty of natural light accentuating the living spaces. Step outside onto the fully fenced 1-acre property and discover a haven of tranquility. Whether you envision a thriving garden, a play area for children, or space for pets to roam, this expansive lot provides endless possibilities. Embrace the breathtaking scenery of Mountain Home, Idaho, known for its picturesque landscapes. Hurry & schedule your viewing today!
